name: DannyBrownTalksPhoenix
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: The purpose of our flash briefing is to be the go-to for all things happening in Phoenix and to get the latest updates in the real estate market. The problem we are solving is to give people additional information about Phoenix and things that they might not already know about - allowing them to keep up with Phoenix culture, events, and the real estate world. Each day will have a different theme — Market Monday, Tip Tuesday, Weekend Update Wednesday, etc. We hope you enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
